00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Common login screen.
The user accesses it from the bottom menu.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:11.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
The user must enter their username
and the corresponding password.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
After completing the fields, the user
clicks the "Login" button.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Logged in. The system redirects
the user to the main page.